00:00:45.420 --> 00:00:47.239
produced something on earth.

00:00:47.239 --> 00:00:49.730
&gt;&gt; I think Area 51 could be possible and could
be real.

00:00:49.730 --> 00:00:52.740
&gt;&gt; You know how there is area 51 and all that
kind of stuff.

00:00:52.740 --> 00:00:55.800
